<Element
comment='Implements standard hazardstatement "signal word": caution, caution1, caution2, danger, warning, and notice. caution is a synonym for caution1. notice is not a recognized signal word in the ISO 3864 standard. @type is the preferred method to specify the signal word, but @level is also supported for compatibility with a pre-DITA1.2 version of the Hazard Statement domain. If no type is specified, caution is assumed. Other types are treated as synonyms for notice.'
